Package sun.jvm.hotspot.ui.tree

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SimpleTreeNode
    A very simple interface for nodes in the SimpleTreeModel.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BadAddressTreeNodeAdapter
    Simple wrapper for displaying bad addresses in the Inspector
    BooleanTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a boolean value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    CharTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a char value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    CStringTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a char value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    CTypeTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates an arbitrary type value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    DoubleTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a double value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    FieldTreeNodeAdapter
    Abstract base class for all adapters for fields of oops
    FloatTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a float value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    LongTreeNodeAdapter
    Encapsulates a long value in a tree handled by SimpleTreeModel
    MetadataTreeNodeAdapter
    An adapter class which allows oops to be displayed in a tree via the SimpleTreeNode interface.
    OopTreeNodeAdapter
    An adapter class which allows oops to be displayed in a tree via the SimpleTreeNode interface.
    RevPtrsTreeNodeAdapter
    Who directly points to this node.
    RootTreeNodeAdapter
    Root oop pointer
    SimpleTreeGroupNode
    Node to which others can be added; suitable for use as root node of graph
    SimpleTreeModel
    A very simple tree model which allows the root to be set, so we can reuse the same model for various types of data; the specialization is contained within the nodes.
